      "text": "Here is an informal ontological conception of an event through definition of skill, role and task. This distinction is entirely independent of the reason, format or content of the event. The manner of participation can only be designed into an event through understanding which factors are fixed and which are changeable. Participation arises from people being in circumstances which exhibit [[Affordance]] to invite agency being enacted."
